{
  "id": "RAW_3b64e7b6",
  "title": "GLM-5.2 上线并开源：专注 Coding 与长程任务",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzI3NzQ0Mg==&mid=2247493980&idx=1&sn=995ae194e71d723b6110fb8c621e618c",
  "date": "2026-06-17 09:11:00",
  "author": "智谱",
  "siteName": "智谱",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260617130303_1445fc6.jpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>今天，我们上线并开源GLM-5.2。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>在全球百万用户参与盲测的前端开发评估系统Code Arena上，</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">GLM-5.2取得全球可用模型第一的表现</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260617130303_7a9d511.png\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>从2025初开始，我们几乎投入全部力量攻关Coding，历时大半年，细扣每一个代码环境的优化，终于迎来代码基座GLM-4.5，年底的GLM-4.7已经成为效果最好的国产Coding模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>但代码还不是AGI，在通往AGI的路上，还有更多的高山需要翻越，迎面而来的就是长程任务。当下最需要模型突破的是完成一个极长的，跨越数天、数周乃至数月的任务执行。当一个模型不知疲倦地在写软件工程代码，本质上是在学习一名顶级软件工程师的思维方式，然后以机器的耐力将其放大。这是对一个又一个职业的重新定义。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>今天GLM-5.2</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">专为长程任务能力而生</span></span></span><span><span>，全新特色包括：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">Solid 1M上下文</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">，</span></span></span><span><span>稳定支撑长程任务</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">更强体感</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">，</span></span></span><span><span>更实用的Coding能力</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">极致Infra优化</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">，</span></span></span><span><span>Day 0运行在国产算力平台</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">MIT开源协议</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">，</span></span></span><span><span>无地域限制，技术平权无国界</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span>1M上下文与长程任务</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>支撑长程任务的第一步是</span><span><span>GLM-5.2必须实现<span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">1M无损上下文</span></span></span></span><span><span>。此前</span><span><span>1M</span><span><span>上下文</span><span><span>大多数</span><span><span>在超过数百K过后就开始劣化，主要问题在于不同时</span><span><span><span><span><span>增强Coding Agent环境及数据的情况下</span></span></span></span></span><span>单纯扩展到1M帮助有限。为此，我们花了几个月时间扩展1M Coding Agent的训练环境，覆盖自动化研究、性能优化等多个领域，使得</span><span><span><span>GLM-5.2在1M上下文</span><span><span><span>的solid表现有时甚至超过Opus（详见</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 109, 244);\"><span><a href=\"https://z.ai/blog/glm-5.2\" target=\"_blank\">https://z.ai/blog/glm-5.2</a></span></span><span><span>）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>1M上下文构成GLM-5.2的长程交付能力</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span>，</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span>多个长程任务基准表明</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">GLM-5.2的表现介于Claude Opus 4.7与4.8之间，是排名最高的开源模型</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></span><span><span>在FrontierSWE（测试AI是否能够像软件工程师在数小时尺度上完成复杂技术项目的测试集）上仅比Opus 4.8低1%，超过GPT-5.5（1%）和Opus 4.7（11%）；不过在SWE-Marathon（考察Agent自主完成超长软件工程的测试集）上确实还需要进一步提高，低于Opus 4.8不少（13%）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260617130303_9ab9ecf.png\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span>在实际体验中，GLM-5.2完成开发、联调、测试到打包上线，完整交付一个覆盖Web、移动端与小程序的多端应用，累计处理88万tokens，几乎用满1M上下文窗口。过去，这样的大型工程需要一支团队协作数周，现在GLM-5.2能在一次长程任务中跑完。</span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span>Coding体感</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>GLM-5.2在前端、后端、长程任务上的成功率相比前一代GLM-5.1都有提升，复杂系统工程与深度调试更稳。在主流编程基准上，GLM-5.2保持开源SOTA，</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">与Claude Opus 4.8处于可比区间</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">例如在Terminal-Bench 2.1（评测AI Agent完成不同类型的计算机终端任务），GLM-5.2比Opus 4.8低4%，相比GLM-5.1提升了17.5%；在MCP-Atlas（大规模工具调研评测的数据集），GLM-5.2比Opus 4.8</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">低0</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">.8%。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260617130303_1c893f6.png\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>在模型发布前夕，我们已提前向GLM Coding Plan用户全员开放，在数十万开发者的编程任务中，开发者反馈GLM-5.2的最大提升集中在：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-radius: 6px;padding: 16px 20px;background: transparent;margin: 16px 0px;text-align: left;\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\"></ul>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">项目级上下文承载更强，能把完整工程放进同一条推理链路里；</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span>长程任务执行更稳定，复杂任务能持续推进，不容易中途跑偏；</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span>生产级工程规范遵循更可靠，能守住团队研发流程里的硬约束；</span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">客户端与移动端工程能力更扎实，不止写App，还能完成真机调试闭环。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span>GLM-5.2还引入了</span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">effort level（思考档位）控制</span></span><span>，可以在能力、速度、成本之间做出平衡。在相近的token预算下，GLM-5.2的Coding能力大致位于Claude Opus 4.7与Claude Opus 4.8之间。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260617130303_4cb4e07.png\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span>极致Infra优化</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span>GLM-5.2的进步来自模型架构、推理系统和训练基础设施的协同设计。我们提出IndexShare，在每四层稀疏注意力层之间复用同一个索引器（indexer），在1M上下文长度下，将单位token的FLOPs</span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">降低至2.9倍</span></span><span>。此外，我们改进了用于投机解码（speculative decoding）的MTP层，将接受长度（acceptance length）</span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">最多提升20%</span></span><span>。训练侧则依赖</span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">自研Slime框架</span></span><span>支撑大规模Agentic RL和OPD训练。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260617130303_67db859.png\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>随着GLM系列的持续迭代与调用量的快速增长，线上服务的稳定性与效率愈发关键。GLM-5.2的线上推理依托多个</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">国产算力平台</span></span></span><span><span>，已在Day 0完成与华为昇腾、平头哥、摩尔线程、寒武纪、昆仑芯、沐曦、海光、壁仞等国产算力平台的推理适配，在国产芯片集群上实现高吞吐、低延迟、大并发的稳定运行。</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">预计下半年昇腾 950 超节点上市后，也将成为GLM-5.2强劲的算力底座</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span>面向开发者与知识工作者</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>GLM-5.2能长时间自主推进更复杂、更长链路的任务，锁定高价值场景，这将改变开发者与知识工作者的工作方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>GLM-5.2在大型重构工程上表现出色。有开发者用Rust从零再造了送人类登月的计算机，将当年65000行、一字未改的登月飞控程序</span><span><span>移植为Rust，整个过程由Agent全自主走完。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>通过我们的Agent产品AutoClaw，GLM-5.2的1M上下文与长程任务能力服务于设计、法务等白领场景，例如一次性写出数十个原型页面，自主迭代和微调，在设计中保持品牌规范与一致性。</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span>开源与使用方式</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>GLM-5.2在Hugging Face与ModelScope开源，</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">模型权重遵循最高权限</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">M</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">IT License</span></span></span><span><span>，可自由下载、部署与商用。vLLM、SGLang、transformers等主流推理框架已经支持。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>同时，GLM-5.2 API已上线，并已纳入GLM Coding Plan，长上下文与长程任务同步升级，全量用户可使用。</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <div style=\"width: 100%;max-width:100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"border: 1px solid #8e8e8e;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding:1em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;caret-color: red;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, C